    return (
        "Visible material culture uses the exact stated date and place from the "
        "cut prompt. Clothing, hairstyle, architecture, tools, vehicles, animals, "
        "weapons, furniture, lighting, terrain, and everyday objects stay "
        "conservative and period-plausible for that culture. "
        f"{surface}"
    )


